OL,3,CMan, 38, guilty of sexual offences
OL,4,Cagainst young girl
OL,6,FA 38-year-old Jersey man has been
OL,7,Ffound guilty of three sexual offences
OL,8,Fagainst a young girl.
OL,10,FDavide Romano was convicted of two
OL,11,Fcounts of sexual touching and one
OL,12,Fcount of causing a sexual act.
OL,14,FThe jury took one hour and 58 minutes
OL,15,Fto reach a unanimous verdict which
OL,16,Fdrew the four-day trial to a close.
OL,18,FGiving evidence via video link, the
OL,19,Fgirl told the court how Romano made
OL,20,Fher play what was described as a
OL,21,Fblindfold game.
