OL,7,Fwill return to the Royal Court on
OL,8,FFriday (14 February) when he will be
OL,9,Ftold about a date for his sentencing.
OL,11,FThe investigating officer, Detective
OL,12,FConstable Jenny Docherty from the
OL,13,FStates of Jersey Police, says: "I
OL,14,Fwelcome the result of the court today.
OL,15,FThese are appalling and calculated
OL,16,Fcrimes.
